com.inqwell.any.client

Class AnyNewListModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.AbstractListModel
      • com.inqwell.any.client.AnyNewListModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, ComboBoxModel, ListModel, MutableComboBoxModel

    public class AnyNewListModel
extends AbstractListModel
implements MutableComboBoxModel
    A model for all swing list-based components.

    This class implements all list models defined in swing, the most complex being javax.swing.MutableComboBoxModel. In this way this class can operate as the model for any of the list component types.

    Version:
    $Revision: 1.3 $
    Author:
    $Author: sanderst $

        This constructor is used when setting up a ComboBox editor for table cells.
